nto Jerusalem, and were come to Bethphage, unto the mount of Olives, then sent Jesus two disciples,","year":33},{"id":"recy7E58WZm4lF2NR","ref":"Matt.21.2","text":"Saying unto them, Go into the village over against you, and straightway ye shall find an ass tied, and a colt with her: loose them, and bring them unto me.","year":33},{"id":"rec5G0Ix1NhvP8pUU","ref":"Matt.21.3","text":"And if any man say ought unto you, ye shall say, The Lord hath need of them; and straightway he will send them.","year":33},{"id":"recmGomnCoChYxtO0","ref":"Matt.21.4","text":"All this was done, that it might be fulfilled which was spoken by the prophet, saying,","year":33},{"id":"recaHkFfMdnQ7tY2A","ref":"Matt.21.5","text":"Tell ye the daughter of Sion, Behold, thy King cometh unto thee, meek, and sitting upon an ass, and a colt the foal of an ass.","year":33},{"id":"rec46lZ1J9mH7snlK","ref":"Matt.21.6","text":"And the disciples went, and did as Jesus commanded them,","year":33},{"id":"recITLnwy7xdoIF7y","ref":"Matt.21.7","text":"And brought the ass, and the colt, and put on them their clothes, and they set him thereon.","year":33},{"id":"recVdEOpK8SY1BdYB","ref":"Matt.21.8","text":"And a very great multitude spread their garments in the way; others cut down branches from the trees, and strawed them in the way.","year":33}]}
